# E-commerce Backend - Implementation Walkthrough

## Summary

Built a complete MERN stack e-commerce backend with user and admin panels, featuring JWT authentication, role-based authorization, and RESTful APIs.

## Project Structure

```
ecommerce_backend/
├── config/
│   └── db.js              # MongoDB connection
├── controllers/           # Business logic (5 files)
├── middleware/            # Auth & error handling (3 files)
├── models/                # Mongoose schemas (4 files)
├── routes/                # API endpoints (5 files)
├── .env                   # Environment variables
├── server.js              # Main entry point
└── README.md              # Documentation
```

